headline: Essex Property Trust: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The San Mateo, California-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $264.5 million, or $3.97 per share, in the period. The average estimate of 11 analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $3.92 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
